title: President discusses South Korea’s inspiring success (City University of Hong Kong)
text: ( Source : City University of Hong Kong ) ​ The President of City University of Hong Kong (CityU) discussed South Korea 's economic and technological advances in his keynote speech at an awards presentation organised by the weekly news magazine
